{
  "stem": "25423.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just wasn't too interested in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, surely I remember that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, the city was bombed again by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was heavy fighting-- not in the city but in the surrounding area-- for almost a week.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the Russians started to withdraw and evacuate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were very many casualties.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as I was in first-aid unit-- so I was going to the places which were bombed out to remove the bodies and help the wounded.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was considerable chaos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we, again, lived in the cellar, as we did in '39-- hunger, lack of water, and the usual.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Germans arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The first day, nothing changed except that the city was decorated with blue and yellow flags because the Ukrainians had the illusion that a Ukraine would be created-- independent Ukraine-- by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the second day was still quiet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But then the pogrom started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's impossible to answer because--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- my father went to the Metropolitan to Archbishop Szeptycki, a highly influential man, and was-- actually prepared a few comments in Polish, which I translated for him in Ukrainian which I had very rudimentary knowledge.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And before going there, he-- his barber came to give him a haircut, which was normal at that time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He put on rabbinical clothes and went there in rabbinical garb, accompanied by two senior members of the community.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said goodbye to my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was lying on the couch and reading a book.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because there were rumors that the Ukrainian population is attacking Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And consequently, he went to his friend asking for intervention.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And after my father left, I just waited for him to come back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was lying on the couch, reading a book, engrossed.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
